### 5. Get Order Details by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/{orderId}

### 6. Get Order Items
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/{orderId}/details

### 7. Update Order Status
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/orders/{orderId}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "PROCESSING"
}

### 8. Get All Orders
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders

### 9. Get Orders by User
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/user/{userId}

### 10. Cancel Order
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/orders/{orderId}

